  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study to evaluate the diagnostic accuracy of a new qualitative aMMP‐8 POC
      test in different periodontal health and disease and as compared to the established
      quantitative laboratory method (ELISA)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      MMP-8 has been reported to reflect the inflammatory status in periodontal tissues and,
      therefore represent as potential biomarkers of periodontitis. A positive aMMP-8 test could be
      an early indicator of these excessive and undesired tissue reactions.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
